<!-- Definition and medical uses -->
'''異煙肼'''，又稱為'''異菸酸酰肼'''（{{lang-en|Isoniazid}}，全名{{lang-en|isonicotinic acid hydrazide}}，簡稱為'''INH'''），為治療[[肺結核|肺結核]]的[[抗生素|抗生素]]<ref name=AHFS2016>{{cite web|title=Isoniazid|url=https://www.drugs.com/monograph/isoniazid.html|publisher=The American Society of Health-System Pharmacists|access-date=8 December 2016|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220231039/https://www.drugs.com/monograph/isoniazid.html|archive-date=20 December 2016}}</ref>。治療開放性肺結核時，常合併投用[[利福平|利福平]]、[[吡嗪酰胺|吡嗪酰胺]]以及[[鏈黴素|鏈黴素]]或[[乙胺丁醇|乙胺丁醇]]二者之一<ref name=WHO2008>{{cite book | title = WHO Model Formulary 2008 | year = 2009 | isbn = 9789241547659 | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | veditors = Stuart MC, Kouimtzi M, Hill SR | hdl = 10665/44053 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | hdl-access=free |page=136 }}</ref>；治療潛伏結核感染時可以單獨使用異煙肼<ref name=AHFS2016/>。本品也可用於治療[[非結核分枝桿菌|非結核分枝桿菌]]（NTM），如{{le|鳥型分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium avium-intracellulare infection}}、{{le|堪薩斯分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium kansasii}}和{{le|異種分枝桿菌|Mycobacterium xenopi}}<ref name=AHFS2016/>。本品的給藥途徑通常為[[口服給藥|口服給藥]]，但也可由[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]]施予<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

<!-- Side effects and mechanism -->
本品常見副作用有{{le|血液中肝臟酵素增加|increased blood levels of liver enzymes}}以及{{le|手腳麻木|numbness in the hands and feet}}<ref name=AHFS2016/>，可能的嚴重副作用為[[肝炎|肝炎]]及急性[[肝衰竭|肝衰竭]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。於[[妊娠|懷孕]]期間使用本品對胎兒的安全性尚屬未知<ref name=Preg2016>{{cite web|title=Isoniazid (Nydrazid) Use During Pregnancy|url=https://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/isoniazid.html|website=www.drugs.com|access-date=10 December 2016|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220231059/https://www.drugs.com/pregnancy/isoniazid.html|archive-date=20 December 2016}}</ref>，在[[母乳哺育|餵母奶]]時應該是安全的<ref name=Preg2016/>。本品可以與[[吡哆醇|吡哆醇]]一起施予以避免其副作用<ref name=Ric2015>{{cite book|last1=Hamilton|first1=Richart|title=Tarascon Pocket Pharmacopoeia 2015 Deluxe Lab-Coat Edition|date=2015|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781284057560|page=49}}</ref>。異煙肼的作用機制為藉由干擾細菌[[細胞壁|細胞壁]]合成，以導致[[殺菌藥|細菌死亡]]<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

<!-- History and culture -->
1952年，異煙肼問世<ref name=Wal2012>{{cite book|last1=Walker|first1=S. R.|title=Trends and Changes in Drug Research and Development|date=2012|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=9789400926592|page=109|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FB_2CAAAQBAJ&pg=PA109|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170910151826/https://books.google.com/books?id=FB_2CAAAQBAJ&pg=PA109|archive-date=2017-09-10}}</ref>。本品名列[[世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單|世界衛生組織基本藥物標準清單]]中<ref name="WHO21st">{{cite book | vauthors = ((World Health Organization)) | title = World Health Organization model list of essential medicines: 21st list 2019 | year = 2019 | hdl = 10665/325771 | author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | id = WHO/MVP/EMP/IAU/2019.06. License: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 IGO | hdl-access=free }}</ref>，[[世界衛生組織|世界衛生組織]]認可為非常重要的人類用藥<ref>{{cite book | vauthors=((World Health Organization)) | year=2019 | title=Critically important antimicrobials for human medicine | edition=6th revision |  author-link = World Health Organization | publisher = World Health Organization | location = Geneva | hdl=10665/312266 | isbn=9789241515528 | hdl-access=free }}</ref>；市面上已有本品的[[通用名藥物|學名藥]]流通<ref name=AHFS2016/>。

